HEADWORD: Signable
<hw>Sign"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Suitable to be
signed; requiring signature; <as>as, a legal document <ex>signable</ex>
by a particular person</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
